rows.label: qst200413_msg0001
rows.name:
I have apprehended all the evildoers
involved in the recent incidents...

rows.label: qst200413_msg0002
rows.name:
Consequently, the woman Ellenora
need worry about her debt no more.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0003
rows.name:
A job very well done, Vasara...
But next time, please do not go off
on your own.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0005
rows.name:
You do realize that your actions could
have endangered the whole party?

rows.label: qst200413_msg0006
rows.name:
And yet, the reason I acted alone was
precisely to avoid endangering you...

rows.label: qst200413_msg0007
rows.name:
Hey, hey.
How about we table this for now.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0008
rows.name:
We should hurry up and bring
Ellenora the good news.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0009
rows.name:
You're right.
Let's go and put her mind at ease!
